com.guardtime.envelope.indexing

Interface IndexProviderFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IncrementingIndexProviderFactory, UuidIndexProviderFactory

    public interface IndexProviderFactory
    IndexProvider factory for creating correct index provider based on default values or provided Envelope as baseline.

      IndexProvider create() 
      IndexProvider create(Envelope envelope)

    • Method Detail

      • create

        IndexProvider create()

      • create

        IndexProvider create(Envelope envelope)
        Creates new IndexProvider based on provided envelope. Verifies the provided Envelope has indexes that are supported by the created IndexProvider and if needed extracts the starting point for indexes.
        Parameters:
        envelope - the base Envelope to use for verifying index type and identifying next indexes.
